WEBVTT

00:01.735 --> 00:03.103
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.103 --> 00:05.205
WHAT WERE YOU DOING
WITH COCAINE IN YOUR TRUCK?

00:05.205 --> 00:07.373
I WASN'T IN MY TRUCK, MOMMY.

00:07.373 --> 00:08.474
HE WAS DRIVING MY CAR.

00:08.474 --> 00:09.976
WHERE'D YOU GET THAT CAR FROM?

00:09.976 --> 00:12.212
THE GUY I WAS
TELLING YOU ABOUT ‐‐

00:12.212 --> 00:13.346
HE GAVE IT TO ME.

00:13.346 --> 00:14.881
ARE YOU SURE
YOU DIDN'T DO THIS?

00:14.881 --> 00:16.717
I DON'T WANT TO GET
THESE LINES CROSSED.

00:16.717 --> 00:19.085
CUT THE CRAP. THE LINES ARE
ALREADY CROSSED, HANNA.

00:19.085 --> 00:23.857
HANNA IS CANDACE'S MOTHER.

00:23.857 --> 00:25.659
[ Voice breaking ] IF YOU
DON'T HELP YOUR BROTHER,

00:25.659 --> 00:26.860
YOU'RE DEAD TO ME.

00:26.860 --> 00:28.529
KATHERYN!

00:32.165 --> 00:34.668
WHAT IS GOING ON?

00:34.668 --> 00:36.402
[ SIGHS ]

00:41.608 --> 00:44.945
I HAVE SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU.

00:44.945 --> 00:48.114
WELL, YOU'VE GOT
MY ATTENTION.

00:51.351 --> 00:56.723
ARE WE JUST GONNA STAND HERE, OR
ARE WE ALL GONNA SING A HYMN?

00:56.723 --> 00:58.224
[ SIGHS ]

00:58.224 --> 01:01.668
YOUR HUSBAND AND I HAVE
BEEN HAVING AN AFFAIR.

01:01.668 --> 01:04.304
‐CANDACE ‐‐
‐NO, JIM.

01:04.304 --> 01:08.508
DON'T STOP HER.

01:08.508 --> 01:10.811
GO ON.

01:10.811 --> 01:15.849
IT'S BEEN GOING ON
FOR WEEKS NOW.

01:15.849 --> 01:18.418
[ LAUGHING ]

01:22.088 --> 01:24.525
VERONICA WAS SO WRONG.

01:24.525 --> 01:28.895
I KNEW DAVID WAS INCAPABLE
OF THIS KIND OF THING.

01:28.895 --> 01:32.298
BUT YOU, DARLING ‐‐ YOU!

01:32.298 --> 01:34.535
[ LAUGHS ]

01:34.535 --> 01:36.102
[ SIGHS ]
CANDACE ‐‐

01:36.102 --> 01:39.339
NO, JIM.
CALL HER BY HER NAME.

01:42.475 --> 01:44.845
CALL HER BY HER NAME.

01:44.845 --> 01:47.981
CANDACE IS MY NAME.

01:47.981 --> 01:51.652
NO, IT ISN'T.

01:51.652 --> 01:52.686
YES, IT IS.

01:52.686 --> 01:54.921
NO, IT ISN'T.

02:01.968 --> 02:05.872
YOUR NAME IS NINE.

02:05.872 --> 02:08.842
YOU'RE NUMBER NINE.

02:08.842 --> 02:11.678
YOU'RE JUST A NUMBER.

02:11.678 --> 02:17.083
YOU'RE JUST A NUMBER ON AN
ASSEMBLY LINE OF MANY ‐‐

02:17.083 --> 02:21.722
YOUNG, PRETTY...

02:21.722 --> 02:23.757
DUMB.

02:23.757 --> 02:26.527
YOU SLEEP WITH
SOMEONE'S HUSBAND,

02:26.527 --> 02:29.830
AND YOU THINK IT'S OKAY, BECAUSE
YOU'RE GONNA TRY TO GET AHEAD.

02:29.830 --> 02:36.036
BUT WHEN YOU DON'T GET YOUR WAY,
YOU TRY AND BRING IT ALL DOWN.

02:36.036 --> 02:37.738
IT DOESN'T WORK THAT WAY, NINE.

02:37.738 --> 02:40.507
YOU AREN'T GONNA GAIN ANYTHING
BY TELLING ME THIS.

02:40.507 --> 02:42.743
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:42.743 --> 02:47.413
JIM, NINE MIGHT BE
THE DUMBEST ONE OF ALL.

02:47.413 --> 02:50.617
YOU THINK I DIDN'T KNOW THERE
WAS A NUMBER NINE?

02:50.617 --> 02:51.685
[ LAUGHS ]

02:51.685 --> 02:53.453
OH, YES, YOU'RE NINE.

02:53.453 --> 02:57.958
AND THERE'LL BE A 10, AN 11,
AND A 12 AND SO ON,

02:57.958 --> 03:01.467
UNTIL HIS PATHETIC, LITTLE PENIS
CAN'T COUNT ANY HIGHER.

03:01.467 --> 03:05.606
IT'S ALREADY HAVING A HARD TIME
COUNTING FOUR INCHES.

03:05.606 --> 03:09.442
YOU ARE JUST AS POWERLESS AS ALL
THE OTHER CHRONOLOGICALS.

03:09.442 --> 03:10.777
I DON'T REALLY UNDERSTAND

03:10.777 --> 03:12.478
WHAT YOU THINK
YOU'RE GONNA ACCOMPLISH

03:12.478 --> 03:14.848
BY DISCLOSING ALL OF THIS
INFORMATION TO ME.

03:14.848 --> 03:18.184
YOU THINK I DIDN'T KNOW
ABOUT YOU?

03:18.184 --> 03:20.220
[ LAUGHING ]

03:23.123 --> 03:25.458
I SAW THE CHEAP LIPSTICK,

03:25.458 --> 03:30.163
AND I ENDURED THE FAINT SMELL

03:30.163 --> 03:35.969
OF THE MOST VULGAR
DRUGSTORE PERFUME I THINK

03:35.969 --> 03:39.272
I HAVE EVER SMELLED ON HIM.

03:39.272 --> 03:41.842
YOU REEK OF IT.

03:41.842 --> 03:46.379
YOU REEK OF THE GUTTER.

03:46.379 --> 03:50.143
YOU ARE AN OFFENSE
TO ALL OF MY SENSES.

03:52.953 --> 03:55.756
WHAT DID HE PROMISE YOU?

03:55.756 --> 03:58.491
OH. THAT LITTLE RED
SPORTS CAR.

03:58.491 --> 04:00.961
I GUESS THAT BELONGED TO YOU.

04:00.961 --> 04:06.372
DID HE TELL YOU
THAT HE WOULD LEAVE ME,

04:06.372 --> 04:10.076
THAT HE WOULD KEEP YOU

04:10.076 --> 04:13.146
AND MAKE YOU HIS PRECIOUS,
KEPT LITTLE GIRL?

04:13.146 --> 04:15.816
[ LAUGHS ]

04:15.816 --> 04:20.286
NINE, I HOLD THE PURSE STRINGS
IN THIS HAND

04:20.286 --> 04:23.256
AND HIS BALLS IN THIS ONE.

04:23.256 --> 04:27.460
YOU ARE A NONFACTOR.

04:27.460 --> 04:31.765
NOW LEAVE MY HOME.

04:31.765 --> 04:35.034
AND YOU CRAWL BACK
TO THE OTHER SIDE OF THE TRACKS

04:35.034 --> 04:40.273
WHERE YOU CAME FROM BEFORE
YOU AWAKEN THE TRUE BITCH IN ME.

04:40.273 --> 04:46.079
♪♪♪♪

04:46.079 --> 04:51.852
♪♪♪♪

04:51.852 --> 04:57.457
AND, NINE, BE CAREFUL
CROSSING THE TRACKS.

04:57.457 --> 05:00.126
THERE MIGHT BE A TRAIN COMING.

05:00.126 --> 05:09.743
♪♪♪♪

05:09.743 --> 05:19.319
♪♪♪♪

05:19.319 --> 05:22.355
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU TRIED TO
ACCOMPLISH BY DOING ALL THAT.

05:22.355 --> 05:23.957
YOU GOT YOUR MONEY,
YOU GOT YOUR CAR,

05:23.957 --> 05:26.459
AND I WANT YOU TO LEAVE
MY FAMILY ALONE,

05:26.459 --> 05:28.428
AND I NEVER WANT
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

05:28.428 --> 05:31.532
YOU PUT THE ONE PERSON
WHO LOVES ME IN PRISON.

05:31.532 --> 05:33.667
YOU GOT THIS ONE WRONG,
CANDACE.

05:33.667 --> 05:34.901
I DIDN'T DO IT.

05:34.901 --> 05:36.503
THEN WHO DID, HMM?

05:36.503 --> 05:38.404
IT'S OVER.

05:38.404 --> 05:39.405
LEAVE.

05:39.405 --> 05:40.974
YOU CAN'T END THIS.

05:40.974 --> 05:42.643
I THINK I JUST DID.

05:42.643 --> 05:44.077
NOW GO.

05:44.077 --> 05:46.747
I'M THE ONE WHO SAYS
WHEN IT'S OVER.

05:46.747 --> 05:49.883
OH, THAT IS SO CANDACE.

05:49.883 --> 05:51.151
WHAT ABOUT ME?

05:51.151 --> 05:52.586
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

05:52.586 --> 05:54.888
I DON'T KNOW.
LET ME SEE.

05:54.888 --> 05:56.389
YOU ARE RECKLESS.

05:56.389 --> 05:58.959
YOU DON'T LISTEN TO ANYBODY.
YOU'RE A MANIAC.

05:58.959 --> 06:02.268
IN FACT, I BELIEVE THAT YOU
WOULD LOCK YOUR ENEMY IN A HOUSE

06:02.268 --> 06:04.838
AND BURN IT TO THE GROUND
EVEN IF YOU WERE IN IT

06:04.838 --> 06:06.206
JUST TO GET BACK AT HIM.

06:06.206 --> 06:07.407
HMM.

06:07.407 --> 06:09.109
BUT, GIRL,
I'M NOT YOUR ENEMY.

06:09.109 --> 06:10.343
YOUR ENEMY'S IN HERE.

06:10.343 --> 06:12.813
THERE'S SOMETHING SERIOUSLY
WRONG WITH YOU.

06:12.813 --> 06:16.683
SOMETHING IS WRONG WITH YOU IF
YOU THINK I'M WEAK AND HELPLESS.

06:16.683 --> 06:19.753
YOUR WIFE MAY NOT CARE,

06:19.753 --> 06:23.890
BUT YOUR DAUGHTER ‐‐
SHE WILL.

06:23.890 --> 06:27.427
I WANT YOU
TO HEAR ME WELL, OKAY?

06:27.427 --> 06:28.862
I'VE ENDURED
ALL OF YOUR THREATS,

06:28.862 --> 06:30.864
EVERY SINGLE, LOVELY THREAT.

06:30.864 --> 06:35.301
BUT SO HELP ME, IF YOU BRING
MY DAUGHTER INTO THIS,

06:35.301 --> 06:39.840
I WILL HAVE YOU MURDERED.

06:39.840 --> 06:42.175
THEN I'LL MAKE SURE AMANDA
HAS A BLACK DRESS.

06:42.175 --> 06:45.445
I'M SERIOUS.
I MEAN IT.

06:45.445 --> 06:50.050
IF YOU GO DOWN THIS ROAD,
I WILL HUNT YOU DOWN.

06:50.050 --> 06:53.419
HMM. BRING IT.

06:53.419 --> 07:02.769
♪♪♪♪

07:02.769 --> 07:12.112
♪♪♪♪

07:12.112 --> 07:15.181
MY COURTROOM IS NOT A CIRCUS.

07:15.181 --> 07:17.083
I WILL NOT TOLERATE
THESE ANTICS

07:17.083 --> 07:19.886
FROM EITHER ONE OF YOU,
DEFENSE OR PROSECUTION.

07:19.886 --> 07:21.287
PULL A STUNT LIKE THAT AGAIN,

07:21.287 --> 07:24.725
I WILL DISMISS THIS JURY AND YOU
CAN EXPLAIN TO THE TAXPAYERS

07:24.725 --> 07:28.094
WHY THIS TRIAL IS COSTING
SO MUCH TO RETRY.

07:28.094 --> 07:29.863
NOW, WHEN WE GET BACK
FROM RECESS,

07:29.863 --> 07:34.735
YOU TWO HAD BETTER HAVE
THIS SITUATION UNDER CONTROL.

07:34.735 --> 07:36.670
JUDGE HARRINGTON.

07:36.670 --> 07:37.571
HELLO.

07:37.571 --> 07:38.572
‐HANNA YOUNG.
‐YES.

07:38.572 --> 07:39.573
YOU REMEMBER ME?

07:39.573 --> 07:41.074
YES, OF COURSE I DO.

07:41.074 --> 07:43.844
WELL, I HOPE YOU DON'T MIND, BUT
MRS. CRYER GAVE ME YOUR NUMBER.

07:43.844 --> 07:45.546
‐MY CELLPHONE NUMBER?
‐YES.

07:45.546 --> 07:47.814
LOOK, I'M SORRY
TO SHOW UP HERE AT YOUR JOB,

07:47.814 --> 07:50.316
BUT I'VE BEEN CALLING HERE
AND CALLING HERE,

07:50.316 --> 07:51.718
AND I JUST KEEP GETTING
THE RUNAROUND.

07:51.718 --> 07:54.354
WELL, I'VE BEEN QUITE BUSY
WITH THE TRIAL.

07:54.354 --> 07:56.022
THOUGHT MY SECRETARY
EXPLAINED THAT.

07:56.022 --> 07:57.591
YES, SIR, SHE DID.

07:57.591 --> 07:59.526
THAT'S WHY
I'VE BEEN WAITING HERE.

07:59.526 --> 08:02.435
AND I WAS JUST HOPING I COULD
GET A MINUTE OF YOUR TIME.

08:02.435 --> 08:04.571
HOW LONG
HAVE YOU BEEN WAITING?

08:04.571 --> 08:06.239
SINCE 5:00 OR 6:00.

08:06.239 --> 08:08.408
‐THIS MORNING?
‐YES, SIR.

08:08.408 --> 08:10.210
WELL, I DIDN'T KNOW WHEN
YOU WERE COMING

08:10.210 --> 08:12.779
OR WHEN YOU WOULD LEAVE, AND
I JUST DIDN'T WANT TO MISS YOU.

08:12.779 --> 08:14.815
AND I DO UNDERSTAND
HOW BUSY YOU ARE.

08:14.815 --> 08:17.150
YES, I AM.

08:17.150 --> 08:19.219
I JUST NEED FIVE MINUTES
OF YOUR TIME.

08:19.219 --> 08:21.955
WOULD YOU JUST SPEAK TO ME IN
PRIVATE FOR JUST A SECOND?

08:21.955 --> 08:23.323
‐MS. YOUNG ‐‐
‐HANNA.

08:23.323 --> 08:24.324
HANNA.

08:24.324 --> 08:26.026
PLEASE, JUDGE,
JUST FIVE MINUTES.

08:26.026 --> 08:30.997
THAT'S ALL I NEED ‐‐ JUST FIVE
MINUTES OF YOUR TIME, PLEASE.

08:30.997 --> 08:32.365
‐ALL RIGHT.
‐THANK YOU.

08:32.365 --> 08:33.667
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

08:33.667 --> 08:35.569
COME ON IN.

08:39.773 --> 08:42.442
HOW CAN I HELP YOU?

08:42.442 --> 08:44.477
WELL, THE LAST TIME WE MET,
YOU SAID YOU WOULD HELP ME

08:44.477 --> 08:47.814
FIND A LAWYER,
AND I HAVEN'T HEARD FROM YOU.

08:47.814 --> 08:49.349
YES, I DID SAY THAT.

08:49.349 --> 08:52.653
AND, AGAIN,
I'VE BEEN QUITE BUSY.

08:52.653 --> 08:55.221
JUDGE, MY SON IS SITTING
IN JAIL.

08:55.221 --> 08:57.724
NOW, HE'S NOT THE KIND OF BOY
THAT CAN HANDLE THAT.

08:57.724 --> 08:58.692
‐HE'S A GOOD KID.
‐YES.

08:58.692 --> 09:00.694
YOU MADE THAT
QUITE CLEAR TO ME.

09:00.694 --> 09:02.168
WELL, MAYBE IF YOU JUST
GIVE ME THE NAME

09:02.168 --> 09:04.137
OF SOME OF THE LAWYERS
THAT YOU SUGGEST,

09:04.137 --> 09:05.939
I COULD CALL THEM MYSELF.

09:05.939 --> 09:07.473
‐MS. YOUNG ‐‐
‐HANNA.

09:07.473 --> 09:11.044
HANNA. I'M TRYING TO
DO YOU A FAVOR.

09:11.044 --> 09:12.946
NOW, THESE GENTLEMEN,
LIKE MYSELF,

09:12.946 --> 09:15.415
ARE QUITE BUSY AND DON'T
APPRECIATE BEING PUSHED.

09:15.415 --> 09:16.983
NO, SIR.
I'M NOT TRYING TO PUSH YOU.

09:16.983 --> 09:19.352
I AIN'T TRYING TO PUSH NOBODY.

09:19.352 --> 09:21.321
I'M JUST A MOTHER
TRYING TO HELP HER SON.

09:21.321 --> 09:22.288
I UNDERSTAND.

09:22.288 --> 09:23.590
A MOTHER WITH NO MONEY.

09:23.590 --> 09:25.191
NO, NO.
I‐I JUST GOT PAID.

09:25.191 --> 09:28.929
AND I PAWNED SOME OF MY JEWELRY
AND SOME THINGS FROM MY HOUSE,

09:28.929 --> 09:30.564
AND I GOT $900, IF THAT HELPS.

09:30.564 --> 09:35.669
HANNA, $900 ISN'T GONNA BUY YOU
ONE HOUR WITH THESE GENTLEMEN.

09:35.669 --> 09:38.805
I DON'T SAY THAT
TO BE CONDESCENDING.

09:38.805 --> 09:43.644
I SAY THAT BECAUSE THESE
ATTORNEYS ARE HIGH‐POWERED.

09:43.644 --> 09:46.913
I HAVE TO CONVINCE THEM TO
TAKE ON YOUR SON'S CASE PRO BONO

09:46.913 --> 09:49.550
IN THE MIDST OF THEIR
VERY BUSY SCHEDULES.

09:49.550 --> 09:51.985
NOW, I HOPE YOU CAN
APPRECIATE MY POSITION.

09:54.621 --> 09:56.356
YES, SIR, I DO.

09:56.356 --> 09:59.325
YOU JUST HAVE TO BE PATIENT.

09:59.325 --> 10:03.504
I CAN BE, BUT I'M WORRIED
ABOUT MY SON.

10:03.504 --> 10:07.808
I UNDERSTAND THAT, AND I HAVE
MADE CALLS ON HIS BEHALF.

10:07.808 --> 10:12.713
I'M WAITING TO HEAR BACK
FROM SOME OF THEM.

10:12.713 --> 10:15.115
OKAY.

10:15.115 --> 10:17.017
I UNDERSTAND.

10:18.619 --> 10:20.086
THANK YOU.

10:27.060 --> 10:28.929
CAN I ASK YOU
ONE MORE THING?

10:32.999 --> 10:36.770
YES, HANNA.

10:36.770 --> 10:39.472
COULD YOU MAYBE HELP ME
GET HIM SOME BLANKETS?

10:39.472 --> 10:42.609
‐BLANKETS?
‐YES.

10:42.609 --> 10:45.812
HE TOLD ME
THEY ONLY GAVE HIM ONE

10:45.812 --> 10:48.281
AND THAT HE WAS
FREEZING AT NIGHT.

10:48.281 --> 10:49.950
[ Voice breaking ]
AND HE'S ALWAYS COLD AT NIGHT,

10:49.950 --> 10:54.788
AND I JUST WANTED HIM
TO BE WARM.

10:54.788 --> 10:57.758
I'M SORRY.
[ SOBS ]

10:57.758 --> 11:01.001
I HAVE BEEN THROUGH A LOT IN MY
LIFE, BUT I CAN'T TAKE THIS!

11:01.001 --> 11:04.505
I'LL ‐‐
I'LL SEE WHAT I CAN DO.

11:04.505 --> 11:07.941
[ SOBS ] I DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON!

11:07.941 --> 11:10.210
OH, PLEASE.
PLEASE, LORD, PLEASE.

11:10.210 --> 11:11.945
PLEASE, JUST HELP MY CHILD.

11:11.945 --> 11:15.649
I'LL CALL YOU AS SOON AS
I HEAR FROM AN ATTORNEY.

11:15.649 --> 11:18.585
OKAY.

11:18.585 --> 11:20.721
WOULD YOU PLEASE PRAY WITH ME,
JUDGE HARRINGTON?

11:20.721 --> 11:23.857
‐I'M SORRY.
‐PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE.

11:26.126 --> 11:27.761
FATHER GOD, WE COME
BEFORE YOU RIGHT NOW.

11:27.761 --> 11:30.664
I COME FOR MY CHILD, LORD GOD.

11:30.664 --> 11:33.734
LORD GOD, I'M PRAYING THAT
ALL TRUTH WILL BE REVEALED ‐‐

11:33.734 --> 11:35.736
THE WHOLE TRUTH, LORD GOD.

11:35.736 --> 11:38.404
I'M PRAYING, AND I'M BINDING UP
THE HAND OF SATAN

11:38.404 --> 11:41.407
THAT IS TRYING
TO DESTROY MY CHILD.

11:41.407 --> 11:43.009
FATHER GOD,
IN THE NAME OF JESUS,

11:43.009 --> 11:45.478
I'M ASKING THAT
YOU MAKE THE WAY CLEAR

11:45.478 --> 11:48.582
AND THE PATH STRAIGHT,
LORD GOD.

11:48.582 --> 11:51.284
LORD GOD, WE KNOW THAT
IT IS ONLY YOU.

11:51.284 --> 11:54.320
IT IS ONLY YOU THAT WE HAVE
IN THIS SITUATION, LORD GOD,

11:54.320 --> 11:56.590
AND I'M ASKING YOU RIGHT NOW
TO LAY HANDS ON

11:56.590 --> 12:00.026
AND PRAY FOR AND BLESS
THE PEOPLE THAT YOU BROUGHT

12:00.026 --> 12:02.769
WHO DIDN'T EVEN KNOW THEY WERE
GONNA BE USED BY YOU, LORD GOD.

12:02.769 --> 12:04.871
I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW. AND I
THANK YOU FOR MRS. CRYER,

12:04.871 --> 12:07.107
WHO BROUGHT HIM TO US.

12:07.107 --> 12:08.642
WE THANK YOU.
WE BLESS YOUR NAME.

12:08.642 --> 12:12.567
IN THE HOLY NAME OF JESUS,
WE PRAY ON BEHALF OF MY CHILD.

12:14.848 --> 12:17.483
I'M ASKING YOU RIGHT NOW.
I'M ASKING YOU, LORD GOD.

12:17.483 --> 12:19.953
I'M ASKING YOU RIGHT NOW.

12:19.953 --> 12:21.988
LORD GOD, PLEASE LET
THE TRUTH BE REVEALED ‐‐

12:21.988 --> 12:24.024
THE WHOLE TRUTH
AND NOTHING BUT THE TRUTH,

12:24.024 --> 12:26.059
AS THEY SAY, LORD GOD.

12:26.059 --> 12:28.795
AMEN.

12:28.795 --> 12:32.432
AMEN.

12:32.432 --> 12:34.434
THANK YOU.

12:34.434 --> 12:36.603
I KNOW YOU DON'T
HAVE TO HELP US.

12:36.603 --> 12:39.372
I KNOW YOU DON'T.

12:39.372 --> 12:43.376
BUT THANK YOU, JUDGE.

12:43.376 --> 12:48.148
GOD BLESS YOU,
AND THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

12:48.148 --> 12:55.756
♪♪♪♪

12:55.756 --> 13:03.336
♪♪♪♪

13:07.574 --> 13:16.983
♪♪♪♪

13:16.983 --> 13:18.318
MORNING, MR. CRYER.

13:18.318 --> 13:19.786
GOOD MORNING.

13:19.786 --> 13:22.122
‐COFFEE?
‐NO. NO, THANK YOU.

13:22.122 --> 13:23.690
CAN I MAKE YOU
SOME BREAKFAST?

13:23.690 --> 13:25.592
NO, NO.
WHOSE BAGS ARE THOSE?

13:25.592 --> 13:26.960
THOSE ARE KATHERYN'S.

13:26.960 --> 13:28.328
SHE'S GOING ON VACATION.

13:28.328 --> 13:29.796
REALLY?

13:29.796 --> 13:31.331
OH, SORRY.

13:31.331 --> 13:33.233
I THOUGHT YOU KNEW.

13:33.233 --> 13:36.236
NO, I DIDN'T KNOW.
WHERE IS SHE?

13:36.236 --> 13:37.403
SHE'S IN THE SUN‐ROOM.

13:37.403 --> 13:40.574
THANKS.

13:40.574 --> 13:45.512
DO YOU REMEMBER WHAT WE USED TO
DO WHEN SHE WENT ON VACATIONS?

13:45.512 --> 13:47.748
THAT MEMORY IS LONG DEAD.

13:47.748 --> 13:50.083
REALLY?

13:50.083 --> 13:52.953
YOU SURE I CAN'T REFRESH
THAT MEMORY OF YOURS?

13:52.953 --> 13:58.058
♪♪♪♪

13:58.058 --> 14:03.169
♪♪♪♪

14:03.169 --> 14:04.805
YOU GOING SOMEWHERE?

14:04.805 --> 14:06.640
WHAT DO YOU CARE, LOVER BOY?

14:06.640 --> 14:07.974
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

14:07.974 --> 14:09.910
DO YOU HAPPEN TO REMEMBER
THAT ON THE 14th OF THIS MONTH,

14:09.910 --> 14:11.812
I'M HOLDING A PRESS CONFERENCE
WHERE I'LL BE ANNOUNCING

14:11.812 --> 14:13.046
I'M RUNNING FOR GOVERNOR?

14:13.046 --> 14:15.448
OH, YOU'RE STILL GONNA RUN?

14:15.448 --> 14:16.617
WHY WOULDN'T I?

14:16.617 --> 14:18.318
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

14:18.318 --> 14:19.586
I THOUGHT MAYBE
YOU'D BE WORRIED

14:19.586 --> 14:21.688
THAT ONE OF YOUR CHRONOLOGICALS
WOULD GO PUBLIC.

14:21.688 --> 14:23.624
OH, I'M SURE IF ANYTHING
LIKE THAT WERE TO HAPPEN,

14:23.624 --> 14:24.758
YOU'D TAKE CARE OF IT.

14:24.758 --> 14:26.259
