WHEN I MET CANDACE ‐‐

14:43.610 --> 14:46.379
NINE.

14:46.379 --> 14:49.249
WHEN I MET HER, I DIDN'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT HER.

14:49.249 --> 14:51.552
