A FRIEND OF AMANDA'S.

14:51.552 --> 14:53.954
AND THAT'S SUPPOSED TO
MAKE IT ALL BETTER,

14:53.954 --> 14:57.991
BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T KNOW
SHE KNEW OUR DAUGH‐TER?

14:57.991 --> 14:58.825
WHAT IS THAT?

14:58.825 --> 15:00.226
YOUR COFFEE, SIR.

15:00.226 --> 15:01.602
