I DIDN'T WANT ANY COFFEE.

15:01.602 --> 15:03.704
NOW TAKE IT OUT OF HERE.

15:03.704 --> 15:06.072
‐YES, SIR.
‐GO ON!

15:07.207 --> 15:08.842
THESE PEOPLE ‐‐ THEY SNOOP.

15:08.842 --> 15:10.110
THEY SNOOP EVERYWHERE.

15:10.110 --> 15:12.312
MY, MY, MY, MY, MY.

15:12.312 --> 15:14.781
LITTLE PARANOID ALL OF A SUDDEN,
AREN'T WE?

15:14.781 --> 15:17.383
