GOING TO BE PROTECTING US

15:17.383 --> 15:20.053
AGAINST THE HELP, I GUESS I'LL
HAVE TO DO IT FROM NOW ON.

15:20.053 --> 15:23.757
OH, I'M THE ONE THAT HAS TO
PROTECT THE STAFF FROM YOU.

15:23.757 --> 15:27.193
YOU'RE THE WOLF.

15:27.193 --> 15:32.533
WHY ARE YOU SO AGITATED
THIS MORNING?

15:32.533 --> 15:34.234
[ SCOFFS ]

15:34.234 --> 15:35.869
YOU LIKE NINE.

15:39.372 --> 15:41.174
ARE YOU GONNA TELL ME WHERE
YOU'RE GOING OR NOT?

15:41.174 --> 15:43.409
