IF YOU'LL ANSWER MINE.

15:43.409 --> 15:45.411
I'M NOT SO SURE
THAT'S A FAIR TRADE.

15:45.411 --> 15:47.180
HOW LONG HAVE YOU
BEEN SEEING NINE?

15:47.180 --> 15:48.582
