15:48.582 --> 15:53.019
YOU MUST THINK YOU'RE TALKING
TO FIVE OR EIGHT OR NINE.

15:53.019 --> 15:54.755
I KNOW YOU.

15:54.755 --> 15:56.823
I SAW YOU IN THAT ROOM.

15:56.823 --> 15:59.325
YOU WERE LIKE A LITTLE BOY
WITH HIS MEMBER

15:59.325 --> 16:01.735
CAUGHT IN A COOKIE JAR.

16:01.735 --> 16:04.805
YOU'RE ENJOYING HER.

16:04.805 --> 16:08.174
YOU WERE TURNED ON BY HER.

16:08.174 --> 16:12.278
