FROM WHAT I GATHER.

16:12.278 --> 16:15.315
WHAT ELSE IS GOING ON IN THOSE
BEADY, LITTLE EYES OF YOURS?

16:15.315 --> 16:16.617
YOU'RE DELUSIONAL.

16:16.617 --> 16:19.119
NO, NO, YOU'RE DELUSIONAL
IF YOU ACTUALLY THINK

16:19.119 --> 16:21.254
THESE YOUNG GIRLS
ARE TURNED ON BY YOU.

16:21.254 --> 16:22.923
YOU'RE OLD.

16:22.923 --> 16:26.459
