MY CHECKBOOK.

16:26.459 --> 16:30.230
$147,000 JUST HAPPENED TO MOVE
OUT OF YOUR ACCOUNT

16:30.230 --> 16:32.198
ON THE DAY NINE
GETS A NEW CAR.

16:32.198 --> 16:33.299
WHAT CAR IS THAT?

16:33.299 --> 16:34.935
