DELIVERED THAT CAR.

16:38.304 --> 16:40.707
HOW DO YOU HAVE ACCESS
TO MY PERSONAL ACCOUNT?

16:40.707 --> 16:44.144
THAT'S LIKE ASKING RAIN
HOW IT GETS WET, DARLING.

16:44.144 --> 16:46.012
I'M KATHERYN CRYER.

16:46.012 --> 16:48.381
IT'S WHAT I DO.

16:48.381 --> 16:50.083
HOW LONG HAVE YOU
BEEN SCREWING NINE?

16:50.083 --> 16:51.885
HOW COME ANY OF THIS
MATTERS TO YOU?

16:51.885 --> 16:53.353
OH, IT MATTERS.

16:53.353 --> 16:54.621
WHY?

16:54.621 --> 16:57.123
THAT WAY I CAN TELL IF
YOUR HEART IS AS INTO HER

16:57.123 --> 16:59.092
AS MUCH AS YOUR
OTHER BODY PARTS.

16:59.092 --> 17:00.393
[ SCOFFS ]

17:00.393 --> 17:02.536
HOW MUCH LONGER IS THIS
MIDLIFE CRISIS GONNA LAST?

17:02.536 --> 17:04.004
I'M NOT HAVING
A MIDLIFE CRISIS.

17:04.004 --> 17:05.872
‐OH, YES, YOU ARE.
‐NO, I'M NOT.

17:05.872 --> 17:10.310
YOU HAVE NEVER BEEN SO RECKLESS,
SO CARELESS!

17:10.310 --> 17:11.945
YOU HAVE ALWAYS BEEN AN ASS,

17:11.945 --> 17:13.814
BUT NEVER AS BIG OF AN ASS
AS YOU ARE RIGHT NOW.

17:13.814 --> 17:16.249
ARE YOU GOING TO TELL ME WHERE
YOU'RE GOING OR NOT?

17:16.249 --> 17:19.720
WHY IS IT SO IMPORTANT TO YOU
WHERE I AM GOING?

17:19.720 --> 17:21.354
IT'S NOT SO IMPORTANT FOR ME

17:21.354 --> 17:22.856
TO KNOW WHERE YOU'RE GOING,
KATHERYN.

17:22.856 --> 17:25.726
WHAT'S IMPORTANT IS THAT I KNOW
HOW LONG YOU'LL BE GONE.

17:25.726 --> 17:27.561
AS LONG AS I WANT TO.

17:27.561 --> 17:29.395
AND YOU MAKE DAMN SURE
YOUR "WANT TO"

17:29.395 --> 17:32.332
IS BACK IN THIS HOUSE
BY THE 14th.

17:32.332 --> 17:34.234
I'M GOING TO WORK.

17:43.510 --> 17:51.885
♪♪♪♪

17:51.885 --> 17:54.387
YES, THIS IS GREAT,
BUT I'M NOT GOING TO ALLOW YOU

17:54.387 --> 17:58.124
TO ARGUE THIS, COUNSELOR.
ARE WE CLEAR?

17:58.124 --> 18:01.301
SHAKE YOUR HEAD, DO SOMETHING
SO I KNOW WE'RE CLEAR.

18:01.301 --> 18:03.203
GET OUT.
THANK YOU.

18:04.705 --> 18:06.372
[ GROANS ]

18:09.175 --> 18:12.278
ROUGH DAY?

18:12.278 --> 18:13.780
I'LL TAKE THAT AS A YES.

18:13.780 --> 18:15.682
ROUGHER NIGHT.

18:15.682 --> 18:17.317
CARE TO EXPLAIN?

18:17.317 --> 18:20.053
CANDACE TOLD KATHERYN ABOUT OUR
ONGOING AFFAIR LAST NIGHT.

18:20.053 --> 18:21.221
WHAT?

18:21.221 --> 18:23.156
CANDACE TOLD KATHERYN ABOUT
OUR AFFAIR LAST NIGHT.

18:23.156 --> 18:24.758
NO, YOU SAID "ONGOING."

18:24.758 --> 18:26.426
ARE YOU STILL INVOLVED
WITH THAT CRIMINAL?

18:26.426 --> 18:27.561
NO, NO, NO.
DAVID, DAVID.

18:27.561 --> 18:29.162
‐ANSWER ME.
‐YES.

18:29.162 --> 18:30.430
ARE YOU INSANE?

18:30.430 --> 18:32.799
I'M NOT GOING TO EXPLAIN THIS
WHOLE THING TO YOU, DAVID.

18:32.799 --> 18:34.568
