18:36.503 --> 18:37.971
AND WHAT DID KATHERYN SAY?

18:37.971 --> 18:39.072
YOU KNOW KATHERYN.

18:39.072 --> 18:41.307
SHE TORE INTO THAT GIRL
LIKE A PIT BULL

18:41.307 --> 18:42.442
WITH A BRAND‐NEW CHEW TOY.

18:42.442 --> 18:43.777
POOR THING
DIDN'T STAND A CHANCE.

18:43.777 --> 18:46.479
NO, WHAT DID KATHERYN
SAY TO YOU?

18:46.479 --> 18:48.014
SHE SAID SHE'S GOING ON
VACATION.

18:48.014 --> 18:49.282
"VACATION"?

18:49.282 --> 18:51.885
NOW, IS THAT A METAPHOR FOR
A DIVORCE OR SEPARATION?

18:51.885 --> 18:54.287
OH, HELL, DAVID, I DON'T KNOW.
YOU KNOW KATHERYN.

18:54.287 --> 18:55.589
