18:55.589 --> 18:56.990
THE 14th IS IN 8 DAYS.

18:56.990 --> 18:58.859
YES, IT IS.
I KNOW THAT.

18:58.859 --> 18:59.993
WHERE IS SHE GOING?

18:59.993 --> 19:02.268
I DON'T KNOW. I ASKED HER.
SHE WOULDN'T TELL ME.

19:02.268 --> 19:04.571
JIM, SHE'S GOT TO BE HERE
ON THE 14th.

19:04.571 --> 19:06.673
I KNOW, I KNOW.
SHE KNOWS THAT.

19:06.673 --> 19:08.775
