ISN'T ABOUT CANDACE.

19:19.319 --> 19:21.722
OH, NO.

19:21.722 --> 19:22.989
WHAT IS IT ABOUT?

19:22.989 --> 19:24.691
YOU HAD YOUR VISITOR.

19:24.691 --> 19:27.127
I HAD MINE.

19:27.127 --> 19:28.795
YOUR MAID HANNA
CAME TO SEE ME.

19:28.795 --> 19:30.797
OF COURSE SHE CAME TO SEE YOU.
SHE'S DESPERATE.

19:30.797 --> 19:32.132
WHY WOULDN'T SHE COME
TO SEE YOU?

19:32.132 --> 19:33.567
