19:33.567 --> 19:37.538
WELL, THAT'S FITTING, SINCE HER
DAUGHTER IS PREYING ON ME.

19:37.538 --> 19:40.173
WHICH, BY THE WAY,
IS A PRAY ON WORDS.

19:40.173 --> 19:41.407
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:43.610 --> 19:47.080
SHE CAME TO ME WITH HER HEART
IN HER HAND FOR HER SON.

19:47.080 --> 19:48.649
AND YOU'RE
TELLING ME THIS WHY?

19:48.649 --> 19:50.884
BECAUSE I'M TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
HOW TO MAKE IT RIGHT.

19:50.884 --> 19:53.219
DON'T TELL ME YOU'RE
GOING SOFT ON ME, DAVID.

19:53.219 --> 19:54.921
