HER BROTHER ‐‐

20:02.468 --> 20:04.738
THEY'RE ALL FAMILY.
THEY'RE ALL IN ON THIS TOGETHER.

20:04.738 --> 20:05.539
THEY SET ME UP.

20:05.539 --> 20:06.573
I DON'T THINK SO.

20:06.573 --> 20:09.109
OH, NOW YOU DON'T THINK SO?

20:09.109 --> 20:11.244
WHEN YOU CAME
RIGHT IN HERE TO MY OFFICE

20:11.244 --> 20:13.246
AND YOU TOLD ME
ALL THE INFORMATION

20:13.246 --> 20:15.716
STANDING RIGHT THERE,
YOU SAID, "YOUR MAID HANNA."

20:15.716 --> 20:17.651
‐I WAS WRONG.
‐HOW COULD YOU BE WRONG?

20:17.651 --> 20:18.685
I KNOW PEOPLE.

20:18.685 --> 20:21.221
I KNOW THAT THIS WOMAN
IS SINCERE.

20:21.221 --> 20:22.288
OH, NOW YOU KNOW PEOPLE,

20:22.288 --> 20:23.857
AND YOU KNOW THAT
THIS WOMAN IS SINCERE?

20:23.857 --> 20:26.827
GIVE ME A BREAK, DAVID.
THIS WOMAN SET ME UP.

20:26.827 --> 20:29.630
I DON'T THINK SO.
I THINK CANDACE IS ROGUE,

20:29.630 --> 20:31.164
DID IT ALL ON HER OWN.

20:31.164 --> 20:33.033
DAVID, THAT'S TOO MUCH
OF A COINCIDENCE.

20:33.033 --> 20:34.400
YOU KNOW THAT.

20:34.400 --> 20:37.838
I RAN A CHECK ON THE MOTHER,
DID A BACKGROUND.

20:37.838 --> 20:40.240
SHE DOESN'T HAVE SO MUCH
AS A PARKING TICKET.

20:40.240 --> 20:42.809
SHE DOESN'T HAVE A CAR,
DAVID!

20:42.809 --> 20:44.811
HOW COULD SHE HAVE
A PARKING TICKET?

20:44.811 --> 20:45.946
WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH YOU?

20:45.946 --> 20:47.347
SHE GOES TO CHURCH
EVERY SUNDAY.

20:47.347 --> 20:48.348
OH!

20:48.348 --> 20:50.450
HAS A PILE OF
MEDICAL BILLS UNPAID.

20:50.450 --> 20:54.988
SHE IS A HARDWORKING WOMAN
TRYING TO HELP HER SON.

20:54.988 --> 20:56.923
AND THE KID IS CLEAN.

20:56.923 --> 21:00.727
APPARENTLY, HE'S HAVING
A HARD TIME IN JAIL.

21:00.727 --> 21:04.304
AND YOU'RE WILLING TO GO
ON RECORD WITH ME RIGHT NOW

21:04.304 --> 21:07.107
AND SAY THAT THIS WOMAN'S HANDS
ARE NOT IN THIS PROBLEM?

21:07.107 --> 21:08.308
YES.

21:08.308 --> 21:09.876
‐YES?
‐YES.

21:09.876 --> 21:11.077
THEN TELL ME SOMETHING, DAVID.

21:11.077 --> 21:13.146
WHY DIDN'T SHE TELL ME CANDACE
WAS HER DAUGHTER?

21:13.146 --> 21:14.280
I DON'T KNOW.

21:14.280 --> 21:16.517
I WOULDN'T CLAIM HER EITHER.

21:16.517 --> 21:21.555
