THAT THAT'S HER CHILD.

21:21.555 --> 21:24.090
IT'S YOUR MESS.
DEAL WITH IT.

21:24.090 --> 21:27.493
OURS, THAT YOU CREATED,
BY THE WAY.

21:27.493 --> 21:30.931
