TO FRAME ANYONE, DID I?

21:30.931 --> 21:31.998
NO, YOU DIDN'T.

21:31.998 --> 21:34.234
NO, I DIDN'T.
SO WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

21:34.234 --> 21:37.037
I DON'T KNOW.

21:37.037 --> 21:40.674
