21:40.674 --> 21:43.043
CAN'T GET IN IT WITHOUT
GETTING MY HANDS DIRTY.

21:43.043 --> 21:45.879
DAVID, DON'T KID YOURSELF.

21:45.879 --> 21:48.048
YOUR HANDS ARE PLENTY DIRTY
ALREADY.

21:48.048 --> 21:51.417
YES.
OUR HANDS ARE DIRTY.

21:51.417 --> 21:54.354
♪♪♪♪

22:07.741 --> 22:09.843
YOU'RE LATE AGAIN.

22:09.843 --> 22:11.277
IS SHE UP?

22:11.277 --> 22:13.413
OH, YEAH.
SHE'S UP.

22:13.413 --> 22:14.681
SHE'S IN THE SUN‐ROOM.

22:14.681 --> 22:16.717
HER BAGS ARE PACKED.

22:16.717 --> 22:17.584
BAGS?

22:17.584 --> 22:18.451
MM‐HMM.

22:18.451 --> 22:19.720
WHY?

22:19.720 --> 22:23.256
YOU DIDN'T FEEL THE TENSION
WHEN YOU WALKED IN HERE?

22:26.292 --> 22:27.794
MRS. CRYER?

22:27.794 --> 22:30.764
HI, HANNA.

22:30.764 --> 22:32.566
HOW IS EVERYTHING?

22:34.801 --> 22:36.169
NOT GOOD.

22:36.169 --> 22:37.704
WHAT'S GOING ON?

22:37.704 --> 22:39.773
I'LL TELL YOU IN A SECOND.

22:39.773 --> 22:41.975
BUT WHY ARE YOUR BAGS PACKED?

22:41.975 --> 22:44.578
I ASKED YOU FIRST.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

22:44.578 --> 22:46.279
I'LL BE FINE.

22:48.381 --> 22:49.683
HOW'S YOUR SON?

22:49.683 --> 22:51.417
NOT WELL.

22:51.417 --> 22:54.254
