TO BE TAKING A TOLL ON HIM.

22:54.254 --> 22:56.122
DID DAVID FIND HIM
A GOOD LAWYER?

22:56.122 --> 22:57.691
NO, NOT YET.

22:57.691 --> 22:58.892
HE DIDN'T?

22:58.892 --> 23:00.594
WELL, HE SAID HE WAS WORKING
ON FINDING HIM ONE,

23:00.594 --> 23:02.035
BUT THEY WON'T RETURN
HIS PHONE CALLS.

23:02.035 --> 23:03.203
OH, THAT'S A LOAD OF CRAP.

23:03.203 --> 23:05.271
NO, I BELIEVE HE'S DOING
HIS BEST TO HELP ME.

23:05.271 --> 23:07.307
NO, HE'S NOT.

23:07.307 --> 23:08.341
WHY DO YOU SAY THAT?

23:08.341 --> 23:10.076
BECAUSE I'M SMELLING
MY HUSBAND'S SCENT

23:10.076 --> 23:12.713
ALL OVER THIS ONE.

23:12.713 --> 23:16.650
