THE SATISFACTION.

24:56.056 --> 24:59.159
YOU'RE REALLY PLANNING ON GOING
THROUGH THIS ALL BY YOURSELF?

24:59.159 --> 25:01.201
NO.

25:01.201 --> 25:02.903
I'LL HAVE YOU.

25:02.903 --> 25:07.273
♪♪♪♪

25:07.273 --> 25:09.009
OKAY.

25:12.312 --> 25:15.115
OKAY.

25:15.115 --> 25:18.519
THANK YOU.

25:18.519 --> 25:20.286
[ SIGHS ]

25:20.286 --> 25:21.655
MADE ALL THE ARRANGEMENTS.

25:21.655 --> 25:23.990
WE'RE GOING TO BE PRIVATE.
MERCY HOSPITAL.

25:23.990 --> 25:26.059
I'M CHECKING IN UNDER AN ALIAS
IN A PRIVATE ROOM.

25:26.059 --> 25:28.094
I'LL BE IN A SECURED FLOOR.

25:28.094 --> 25:34.801
NO ONE KNOWS ABOUT THIS BUT
THE DOCTORS, MYSELF, AND YOU.

25:34.801 --> 25:37.638
AND YOU'RE SURE YOU DON'T
WANT ME TO TELL YOUR FAMILY?

25:37.638 --> 25:39.873
I AM SURE.

25:39.873 --> 25:44.110
I UNDERSTAND ABOUT YOUR HUSBAND
AND MAYBE EVEN YOUR SON,

25:44.110 --> 25:45.411
BUT WHAT ABOUT AMANDA?

25:45.411 --> 25:49.149
AMANDA CAN'T HANDLE IT.

25:49.149 --> 25:50.951
SHE CAN'T HANDLE MUCH.

25:50.951 --> 25:53.820
SHE'S SUCH A FRAGILE
LITTLE THING.

25:53.820 --> 26:01.868
♪♪♪♪

26:01.868 --> 26:09.910
♪♪♪♪

26:09.910 --> 26:12.212
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

26:12.212 --> 26:14.548
I HAD TO CLEAR MY MIND.

26:14.548 --> 26:17.017
I GOT MY EXAM BACK.

26:17.017 --> 26:19.986
LOOK, AMANDA, I DON'T HAVE TIME
FOR THIS TODAY, OKAY?

26:19.986 --> 26:23.389
IF YOU CAN'T PASS YOUR COURSES,
THEN THAT'S YOUR PROBLEM.

26:23.389 --> 26:25.458
AND IF YOU WANT TO QUIT
LAW SCHOOL, THEN DO IT.

26:25.458 --> 26:27.160
AND IF YOU CAN'T
STAND UP TO YOUR FAMILY,

26:27.160 --> 26:28.862
THEN THAT IS YOUR PROBLEM.

26:28.862 --> 26:30.964
I HAVE A LOT ON MY MIND,

26:30.964 --> 26:34.535
AND I AM SICK OF YOUR WHINING.

26:34.535 --> 26:38.304
SORRY.

26:38.304 --> 26:40.006
[ GROANS ]

26:42.442 --> 26:47.848
