26:54.888 --> 27:01.802
♪♪♪♪

27:05.906 --> 27:07.774
‐THAT SHOULD DO IT.
‐OKAY.

27:07.774 --> 27:09.475
Hanna: I'LL GET THE GARDENER TO
HELP ME PUT THEM IN THE CAR.

27:09.475 --> 27:11.077
Katheryn: THANK YOU.

27:11.077 --> 27:13.479
WE'LL STOP BY YOUR HOUSE TO
PICK UP YOUR BAGS, OKAY?

27:13.479 --> 27:15.115
‐OKAY.
‐GREAT.

27:15.115 --> 27:16.683
‐CELINE?
‐YES, MA'AM?

27:16.683 --> 27:18.184
I'D LIKE TEA IN THE SUN‐ROOM,
PLEASE.

27:18.184 --> 27:19.385
YES, MA'AM.

27:19.385 --> 27:21.321
MAKE IT FOR TWO. VERONICA
SHOULD BE HERE ANY MINUTE.

27:21.321 --> 27:23.289
YES, MA'AM.

27:25.659 --> 27:30.096
[ SCOFFS ] YOU'RE GOING
ON VACATION WITH HER?

27:30.096 --> 27:32.398
YES.

27:32.398 --> 27:35.602
I HAVE A QUESTION.

27:35.602 --> 27:36.803
WHAT?

27:36.803 --> 27:39.372
SHE'S NEVER TAKEN ME
ON VACATION.

27:39.372 --> 27:41.074
THAT'S NOT A QUESTION.

27:41.074 --> 27:42.576
WHY ARE YOU GOING?

27:42.576 --> 27:44.845
YOU SHOULD ASK HER.

27:44.845 --> 27:45.979
THIS IS JUST GREAT.

27:45.979 --> 27:47.013
[ LAUGHS ]
THIS IS JUST GREAT.

27:47.013 --> 27:48.448
YOU'VE BEEN HERE
ONLY A FEW WEEKS,

27:48.448 --> 27:50.784
AND YOU'VE TOTALLY
TAKEN OVER, AND NOW ‐‐

27:50.784 --> 27:52.285
NOW YOU'RE MY BOSS?

27:52.285 --> 27:54.487
‐I'M NOT YOUR BOSS.
‐WELL, YOU ACT LIKE IT, HANNA.

27:54.487 --> 27:55.689
HOW'S THAT?

27:55.689 --> 27:57.658
YOU GO EVERYWHERE WITH HER.

27:57.658 --> 27:59.826
APPARENTLY, NOW YOU'RE
GOING ON VACATION!

27:59.826 --> 28:02.335
CELINE, I'M JUST TRYING
TO KEEP MY JOB.

28:02.335 --> 28:05.138
HANNA, THERE'S
KEEPING YOUR JOB,

28:05.138 --> 28:08.008
AND THEN THERE'S OVERBOARD,
AND THIS IS OVERBOARD.

28:08.008 --> 28:10.977
CELINE, I'M NOT
IN THE MOOD FOR THIS.

28:10.977 --> 28:12.445
OH, WAIT.

28:12.445 --> 28:15.015
OH, I KNOW WHAT IT IS.

28:15.015 --> 28:17.417
‐YOU'RE SLEEPING TOGETHER.
‐ARE YOU CRAZY?

28:17.417 --> 28:19.485
WELL, THAT'S THE ONLY THING
THAT MAKES SENSE TO ME.

28:19.485 --> 28:21.221
YOU'RE...BOTH LESBIANS.

28:21.221 --> 28:22.355
I'MMA FORGET YOU SAID THAT.

28:22.355 --> 28:23.924
NO, YOU CAN TELL ME.
IT'S OKAY.

28:23.924 --> 28:26.960
I'M NOT A LESBIAN, AND I'M NOT
GONNA TELL YOU ANYTHING.

28:26.960 --> 28:29.630
SEE, THAT LITTLE REVERSE
PSYCHOLOGY DOESN'T WORK ON ME.

28:29.630 --> 28:32.566
YOU MADE UP ALL THAT STUFF SO
I WOULD TELL YOU SOMETHING.

28:32.566 --> 28:37.003
SEE, I'VE BEEN DOING THIS A LONG
TIME, AND YOU DO NOT FOOL ME.

28:37.003 --> 28:41.041
SHE'S NOT YOUR FRIEND,
AND DON'T YOU FORGET THAT.

28:41.041 --> 28:44.110
THERE ARE LINES TO BE CROSSED,
HANNA, AND WHEN THEY ARE...

28:44.110 --> 28:45.278
[LAUGHS]

28:45.278 --> 28:47.681
...YOU ARE GOING TO BE
DEEPLY HURT, AND I,

28:47.681 --> 28:51.484
CELINE GONZALEZ, WILL NOT BE
THERE TO PICK UP THE PIECES.

28:51.484 --> 28:52.819
GOT IT?

28:52.819 --> 28:58.959
♪♪♪♪

28:58.959 --> 29:00.967
Veronica: KAT.

29:00.967 --> 29:03.336
‐HI.
‐HI.

29:03.336 --> 29:05.305
CAME AS SOON AS
I GOT YOUR CALL.

29:05.305 --> 29:07.541
THANK YOU.
I APPRECIATE THAT.

29:07.541 --> 29:10.343
SURE.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

29:10.343 --> 29:12.746
HAS DAVID BEEN
REAL BUSY LATELY?

29:12.746 --> 29:14.147
SAME AS USUAL.

29:14.147 --> 29:15.348
NOTHING OUT OF THE ORDINARY.

29:15.348 --> 29:16.583
I THOUGHT SO.

29:16.583 --> 29:19.385
WOULD YOU LIKE TO SHARE?

29:19.385 --> 29:22.823
WELL, I ASKED HIM
TO HELP HANNA.

29:22.823 --> 29:24.257
HELP HER WITH WHAT?

29:24.257 --> 29:26.760
HER SON IS IN JAIL.

29:26.760 --> 29:27.661
REALLY?

29:27.661 --> 29:28.995
HE'S INNOCENT.

29:28.995 --> 29:30.831
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

29:30.831 --> 29:32.733
BECAUSE I TRUST HANNA.

29:32.733 --> 29:35.268
SHE'S A TRUTH TELLER.

29:35.268 --> 29:37.370
WELL, WHAT DOES THIS
HAVE TO DO WITH DAVID?

29:37.370 --> 29:39.405
HE CAN'T TAKE THIS
INTO HIS COURTROOM.

29:39.405 --> 29:42.576
NO, HE CAN'T, BUT I ASKED HIM
TO HELP HANNA FIND A LAWYER,

29:42.576 --> 29:44.477
AND HE HASN'T RETURNED
ANY OF MY CALLS.

29:44.477 --> 29:46.580
‐THAT'S ODD.
‐YEAH.

29:46.580 --> 29:48.248
JIM'S ALL IN IT.

29:48.248 --> 29:49.850
MAYBE THEY DON'T WANT
TO HELP HER.

29:49.850 --> 29:51.618
WHY WOULDN'T THEY WANT
TO HELP HER?

29:51.618 --> 29:53.386
I DON'T KNOW. JIM HAS A BEE
IN HIS BONNET

29:53.386 --> 29:55.455
FOR HANNA THESE DAYS.
I'M NOT QUITE SURE.

29:55.455 --> 29:57.023
THAT STILL DOESN'T EXPLAIN
WHY DAVID

29:57.023 --> 29:58.424
WOULDN'T HELP YOU
FIND A LAWYER.

29:58.424 --> 30:00.601
BECAUSE JIM HAS PROBABLY
TOLD HIM NOT TO.

30:00.601 --> 30:02.669
THAT'S WHY.

30:02.669 --> 30:05.005
HENCE WHY
I'VE ASKED YOU OVER.

30:06.673 --> 30:08.775
HAVE A SEAT.

30:08.775 --> 30:10.210
OKAY.

30:13.413 --> 30:15.381
WHAT IS IT?

30:15.381 --> 30:16.817
I NEED YOUR HELP.

30:19.953 --> 30:23.189
I MEAN REALLY NEED YOUR HELP.

30:25.258 --> 30:27.060
OH, NO.

30:27.060 --> 30:28.494
[ Laughing ] NO.

30:28.494 --> 30:29.930
COME ON!

30:29.930 --> 30:32.132
I HAVEN'T PRACTICED LAW
IN THREE YEARS.

30:32.132 --> 30:33.934
BUT YOU STILL HAVE
YOUR LICENSE INTACT.

30:33.934 --> 30:35.902
BUT I AM RETIRED.

30:35.902 --> 30:38.605
I HAVE MY
REHAB FACILITIES TO RUN.

30:38.605 --> 30:41.374
VERONICA, SHE NEEDS OUR HELP.

30:41.374 --> 30:43.443
WHAT DID THE CHILD DO?

30:43.443 --> 30:45.111
DRUG POSSESSION.

30:45.111 --> 30:46.479
FIGURES.

30:46.479 --> 30:48.014
HE'S INNOCENT.

30:48.014 --> 30:51.652
KATHERYN, I GREW UP AROUND
THESE KINDS OF PEOPLE.

30:51.652 --> 30:53.019
I'M FROM THIS.

30:53.019 --> 30:56.322
THEY NEVER DO IT,
BUT THEY ARE ALWAYS GUILTY.

30:56.322 --> 30:58.559
I DO NOT NEED
ANOTHER HISTORY LESSON

30:58.559 --> 31:00.393
ON YOUR MEAN STREETS
OF CHICAGO.

31:00.393 --> 31:01.802
BUT YOU SHOULD LISTEN.

31:01.802 --> 31:04.738
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND THIS
UNLESS YOU'VE LIVED IT.

31:04.738 --> 31:05.972
I NEED TO HELP HER.

31:05.972 --> 31:07.340
WHY CAN'T HE JUST ADMIT IT

31:07.340 --> 31:09.042
AND TAKE A PLEA
WITH A PUBLIC DEFENDER?

31:09.042 --> 31:10.276
YOU KNOW AS WELL AS I DO

31:10.276 --> 31:12.879
THAT PUBLIC DEFENDERS
ARE OVERWORKED.

31:12.879 --> 31:15.215
AND IT'S VERY DIFFICULT
FOR THEM TO BE EFFECTIVE.

31:15.215 --> 31:17.918
COME ON!

31:17.918 --> 31:19.820
I NEED YOU.

31:19.820 --> 31:22.455
‐WHY WOULD I DO THIS?
‐BECAUSE HE'S A GOOD BOY.

31:22.455 --> 31:23.990
‐HAVE YOU MET HIM?
‐NO.

31:23.990 --> 31:25.458
THEN HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

31:25.458 --> 31:27.093
I BELIEVE HANNA.

31:27.093 --> 31:28.194
KAT, PLEASE.

31:28.194 --> 31:31.665
HE HAS A BAIL HEARING
IN A DAY OR SO.

31:31.665 --> 31:34.400
PLEASE, VERONICA.

31:34.400 --> 31:35.969
SHE'S DESPERATE.

31:40.406 --> 31:43.376
I HAVEN'T BEEN IN A COURTROOM
IN YEARS.

31:43.376 --> 31:44.611
YOU CAN HANDLE IT.

31:44.611 --> 31:47.480
I KNOW I CAN HANDLE IT.

31:47.480 --> 31:49.916
BUT WHY SHOULD I?

31:49.916 --> 31:52.653
BECAUSE SHE NEEDS OUR HELP.

31:52.653 --> 31:55.055
[ GROANS ]

31:55.055 --> 31:57.758
[ SIGHS ]

31:57.758 --> 31:59.359
OKAY.

31:59.359 --> 32:00.834
OKAY!

32:00.834 --> 32:04.571
I WILL DO THIS FOR YOU.

32:04.571 --> 32:07.273
ONE OF A KIND, VERONICA.
ONE OF A KIND.

32:07.273 --> 32:08.775
[ SIGHS ]

32:08.775 --> 32:11.111
HANNA, WILL YOU
COME IN, PLEASE?

32:11.111 --> 32:15.215
YOU ARE GONNA
OWE ME BIG‐TIME.

32:15.215 --> 32:16.683
YES, MA'AM?

32:16.683 --> 32:18.952
YOU REMEMBER VERONICA.

32:18.952 --> 32:21.688
YES, MA'AM, I DO.
MRS. HARRINGTON.

32:21.688 --> 32:26.126
BUT WHAT YOU MAY NOT KNOW IS
THAT VERONICA IS ONE OF THE ‐‐

32:26.126 --> 32:27.460
WAS.

32:27.460 --> 32:32.165
IS ONE OF THE BEST CRIMINAL
ATTORNEYS IN THIS TOWN.

32:32.165 --> 32:36.302
AND SHE'S AGREED
TO HELP YOU.

32:36.302 --> 32:38.471
OH, THANK GOD.

32:38.471 --> 32:43.043
THANK YOU,
AND THANK YOU SO MUCH.

32:43.043 --> 32:46.580
UH, I WILL NEED TO KNOW
EVERYTHING THERE IS TO KNOW

32:46.580 --> 32:49.449
ABOUT THE CASE AND YOUR SON.

32:49.449 --> 32:50.551
ABSOLUTELY.

32:50.551 --> 32:52.519
WE'LL MEET TOMORROW.

32:52.519 --> 32:53.854
AND IN THE MEANTIME,

32:53.854 --> 32:57.524
I WILL FIND OUT EVERYTHING THERE
IS TO KNOW ABOUT THIS CASE.

32:57.524 --> 33:01.535
♪♪♪♪

33:01.535 --> 33:04.370
CAN YOU WRITE...

33:04.370 --> 33:07.307
DOWN HIS FULL NAME,

33:07.307 --> 33:10.544
SOCIAL SECURITY NUMBER,
AND DATE OF BIRTH?

33:10.544 --> 33:13.914
SHE'S GONNA TAKE
VERY GOOD CARE OF YOU, HANNA.

33:13.914 --> 33:15.982
THANK YOU.

33:15.982 --> 33:18.451
CAN YOU WRITE
THOSE THINGS DOWN, PLEASE?

33:18.451 --> 33:20.253
YES.
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:20.253 --> 33:22.188
YES, MA'AM, I CAN.

33:22.188 --> 33:27.127
♪♪♪♪

33:27.127 --> 33:30.764
IF THIS BOY IS NOT CLEAN,

33:30.764 --> 33:34.034
IT'S GONNA BE ME AND YOU,
KATHERYN CRYER.

33:40.841 --> 33:42.676
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

33:44.377 --> 33:45.979
[ SIGHS ]
JIM...

33:52.052 --> 33:54.087
YOU GOT AN "A."

34:06.640 --> 34:09.209
AMANDA...

34:09.209 --> 34:11.645
[ SIGHS ]
SORRY.

34:11.645 --> 34:15.315
I HAD A ROUGH DAY.

34:15.315 --> 34:16.883
[ KNOCK AT DOOR ]

34:16.883 --> 34:19.753
‐WHO IS IT?
‐CANNON.

34:23.524 --> 34:25.358
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

34:25.358 --> 34:27.127
UH, HI.
HEY, I DIDN'T, UH ‐‐

34:27.127 --> 34:28.762
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE GONNA BE HERE.

34:28.762 --> 34:29.930
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

34:29.930 --> 34:32.999
I CAME BY TO, UH,
GIVE AMANDA A MAKE‐UP EXAM.

34:32.999 --> 34:34.801
A MAKE‐UP EXAM?

34:34.801 --> 34:36.703
‐SHE GOT AN "A."
‐YES, SHE DID.

34:36.703 --> 34:40.807
BUT, UH, THIS IS ANOTHER ONE.

34:40.807 --> 34:43.544
HOW MANY TIMES
HAVE YOU BEEN HERE?

34:43.544 --> 34:44.711
MY SECOND.

34:44.711 --> 34:47.013
DID YOU SLEEP WITH HER?

34:47.013 --> 34:48.048
YOU WEARING A WIRE?

34:48.048 --> 34:50.717
DON'T TOUCH ME.

34:50.717 --> 34:52.953
DID YOU SLEEP WITH HER?

34:52.953 --> 34:55.188
YOU KNOW, SHE'S A PRETTY GOOD
LITTLE ACTRESS.

34:55.188 --> 34:56.990
SHE TRIED ‐‐ TRIED TO PRETEND
THAT SHE WASN'T INTO IT,

34:56.990 --> 34:59.092
BUT EVENTUALLY, SHE CAVED IN.

34:59.092 --> 35:00.466
I DIDN'T KNOW
SHE WORKED FOR YOU.

35:00.466 --> 35:01.735
SHE DOESN'T.

35:01.735 --> 35:04.170
SHE DOESN'T?
[ SCOFFS ]

35:04.170 --> 35:05.205
WHAT DID YOU TELL HER?

35:05.205 --> 35:06.707
NOT MUCH, YOU KNOW?

35:06.707 --> 35:10.611
BEEN HERE A COUPLE OF TIMES WITH
YOU DURING YOUR FRESHMAN YEAR.

35:10.611 --> 35:14.014
OH, I GOT TO TELL YOU,
SHE FAILS EVERY TEST.

35:14.014 --> 35:16.617
SHE IS SO SWEET AND PURE.

35:16.617 --> 35:18.451
I JUST WANT TO
TAKE A BITE OUT OF HER.

35:18.451 --> 35:20.186
SHE'S LIKE VIRGIN‐LIKE.

35:20.186 --> 35:21.522
IS SHE HERE RIGHT NOW?

35:21.522 --> 35:23.223
WHY DON'T WE HAVE A THREESOME?

35:23.223 --> 35:25.325
‐COME ON!
‐GOODBYE.

35:25.325 --> 35:27.427
WHAT?
WHAT'S THE MATTER?

35:27.427 --> 35:28.562
GOODBYE!

35:28.562 --> 35:29.896
WHAT?
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

35:29.896 --> 35:31.297
YOU TWO ARE JUST ‐‐

35:31.297 --> 35:32.933
YOU TWO ARE JUST BEGGING
TO FAIL, AREN'T YOU?

35:32.933 --> 35:34.000
YOU LISTEN TO ME.

35:34.000 --> 35:35.702
AH.

35:35.702 --> 35:40.541
SHE BETTER GET AN "A" PLUS
ON EVERY EXAM FROM NOW ON.

35:40.541 --> 35:44.410
AND YOU BETTER NEVER COME NEAR
HER OR MYSELF EVER AGAIN.

35:44.410 --> 35:48.582
IF YOU DO, THE ENTIRE FACULTY
WILL KNOW ABOUT YOU.

35:48.582 --> 35:49.983
FAIR ENOUGH, FAIR ENOUGH.

35:49.983 --> 35:53.353
YOU KNOW, UH...
THEY MAY NOT KNOW ABOUT ME,

35:53.353 --> 35:55.756
BUT THEY CERTAINLY KNOW
ABOUT YOU TWO.

35:55.756 --> 35:59.793
YOU SURE? YOU SURE
YOU DON'T WANT TO DO THIS?

35:59.793 --> 36:01.094
YOU KNOW WHAT?

36:01.094 --> 36:04.470
ON SECOND THOUGHT, JUST ‐‐
JUST WAIT RIGHT THERE, OKAY?

36:04.470 --> 36:06.106
‐UH‐HUH.
‐OKAY.

36:06.106 --> 36:12.613
♪♪♪♪

36:12.613 --> 36:14.280
HMM.

36:14.280 --> 36:16.683
♪♪♪♪

36:16.683 --> 36:17.884
AH!

36:17.884 --> 36:19.620
HERE WE ARE.

36:19.620 --> 36:21.421
YOU REMEMBER THAT?

36:21.421 --> 36:23.256
HMM.
OH, THIS.

36:23.256 --> 36:25.425
THEY ‐‐ THEY WOULD LOVE
TO SEE THAT ONE.

36:25.425 --> 36:26.927
DIAPER BOY?
HMM?

36:26.927 --> 36:29.495
I HAVE CAMERAS
ALL OVER THIS PLACE.

36:29.495 --> 36:31.665
I HAVE BEEN FILMING YOU
SINCE DAY ONE.

36:31.665 --> 36:34.801
I HAVE BACKUP ON EVERYTHING
YOU HAVE DONE.

36:34.801 --> 36:39.272
♪♪♪♪

36:39.272 --> 36:40.240
YOU CAN HAVE THOSE.

36:40.240 --> 36:41.675
I HAVE DUPLICATES.

36:41.675 --> 36:44.978
♪♪♪♪

36:44.978 --> 36:47.047
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

36:47.047 --> 36:49.482
AMANDA!

36:49.482 --> 36:53.186
AMANDA, ARE YOU SLEEPING?

36:53.186 --> 36:54.387
AMANDA?

36:54.387 --> 37:02.669
♪♪♪♪

37:02.669 --> 37:10.910
♪♪♪♪

37:10.910 --> 37:13.179
ARE YOU SCARED?

37:13.179 --> 37:15.615
YES.

37:15.615 --> 37:19.018
DID YOU HAVE
THE SAME SURGERY?

37:19.018 --> 37:21.387
YES.

37:21.387 --> 37:23.924
BUT MY EXPERIENCE IN THE
HOSPITAL WASN'T LIKE THIS.

37:23.924 --> 37:26.092
[ LAUGHS ]

37:26.092 --> 37:28.995
THIS ROOM IS NICER
THAN MY ROOM AT HOME.

37:28.995 --> 37:32.733
IT COSTS AS MUCH AS MINE, AND
I DON'T CARE HOW NICE IT IS.

37:32.733 --> 37:34.568
I DON'T WANT TO BE HERE.

37:36.336 --> 37:37.871
IT'S OKAY TO BE SCARED.

37:37.871 --> 37:40.974
GOOD.
BECAUSE I AM.

37:40.974 --> 37:42.943
YOU ALWAYS SEEM SO STRONG.

37:42.943 --> 37:45.546
YOU CAN'T SHOW WEAKNESS
IN MY FAMILY, HANNA.

37:45.546 --> 37:48.248
THEY PREY ON THE WEAK.

37:48.248 --> 37:49.516
I UNDERSTAND THAT.

37:49.516 --> 37:50.483
DO YOU?

37:50.483 --> 37:52.352
YES.

37:52.352 --> 37:54.254
AND YOU'RE IN THE BEST HANDS.

37:54.254 --> 37:57.223
I LOOKED UP THIS DOCTOR
WHEN I WAS DIAGNOSED.

37:57.223 --> 38:02.302
OOH, I WANTED HIM SO BAD,
BUT I COULDN'T AFFORD HIM.

38:02.302 --> 38:05.138
I DIDN'T HAVE
ANY HEALTH INSURANCE.

38:05.138 --> 38:08.141
YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE.

38:08.141 --> 38:09.610
I AM SO TIRED.

38:09.610 --> 38:11.578
MNH‐MNH.
DON'T TALK LIKE THAT.

38:11.578 --> 38:13.514
‐I AM, HANNA.
‐YEAH, I KNOW.

38:13.514 --> 38:15.448
BUT, SEE, MOST OF THIS FIGHT
IS IN YOUR MIND.

38:15.448 --> 38:18.118
YOU CAN'T GIVE INTO IT,
OR IT'LL TAKE YOU UNDER.

38:18.118 --> 38:20.921
I'M NOT GONNA DIE.
THAT WOULD BE TOO EASY.

38:20.921 --> 38:24.758
I KNOW YOU'RE NOT GONNA DIE.

38:24.758 --> 38:26.426
[ SIGHS ]

38:26.426 --> 38:29.295
I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D BE HERE AT 53.

38:29.295 --> 38:31.264
WELL, LIFE HAS
A WAY OF TAKING US

38:31.264 --> 38:33.900
WHERE WE NEVER THOUGHT
WE'D BE.

38:33.900 --> 38:37.070
I KNOW THAT FEELING
ALL TOO WELL.

38:40.006 --> 38:42.576
ANYTHING I CAN GET FOR YOU?

38:42.576 --> 38:44.811
YOU THINK GOD HEARS
ALL OUR PRAYERS, HANNA?

38:44.811 --> 38:47.814
I KNOW IT.

38:47.814 --> 38:49.750
YOU PRAY FOR ME?

38:49.750 --> 38:51.117
I ALREADY HAVE.

38:51.117 --> 38:52.418
AND MY FAMILY.

38:52.418 --> 38:54.354
[ CHUCKLES ]

38:54.354 --> 38:57.123
PLEASE, PRAY FOR MY FAMILY.

38:57.123 --> 38:58.525
IT'S ALREADY DONE.

38:58.525 --> 39:01.802
[ CHUCKLES ]

39:01.802 --> 39:03.770
SING THAT SONG TO ME.

39:03.770 --> 39:06.472
WHAT SONG?

39:06.472 --> 39:08.542
THAT SONG YOU SING
WHEN YOU'RE CLEANING HOUSE

39:08.542 --> 39:10.210
AND YOU DON'T THINK
ANYBODY'S AROUND.

39:10.210 --> 39:11.311
YOU HEARD ME?

39:11.311 --> 39:12.846
YEAH, I DID.

39:12.846 --> 39:15.649
YOU HAVE A BEAUTIFUL
VOICE, HANNA.

39:15.649 --> 39:17.150
THANK YOU.

39:17.150 --> 39:18.752
WHAT'S THE NAME OF THAT SONG?

39:18.752 --> 39:21.354
SOME SONG MY GRANDMOTHER
USED TO SING.

39:21.354 --> 39:23.790
IT'S CALLED
"A LEAK IN THIS OLD BUILDING,"

39:23.790 --> 39:26.827
‐SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
‐[ LAUGHS ]

39:26.827 --> 39:29.630
SING IT TO ME.

39:29.630 --> 39:31.397
HOW ABOUT WE SING IT
TOGETHER?

39:31.397 --> 39:33.133
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU'D HAVE TO TEACH IT TO ME.

39:33.133 --> 39:35.702
I'M NOT TOO FAMILIAR
WITH MY NEGRO SPIRITUALS.

39:35.702 --> 39:37.203
I DIDN'T THINK YOU WERE.

39:37.203 --> 39:41.241
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

39:41.241 --> 39:42.543
SING IT, HONEY.

39:46.146 --> 39:50.383
♪♪ THERE'S A LEAK
IN THIS OLD BUILDING ♪♪

39:50.383 --> 39:54.855
♪♪ AND MY SOUL
